			</p>
			<ul class='rslides rslides1'>
				<li
					class='overlay rslides1_on'
					id='rslides1_s0'
					style='display: block; float: left; position: relative; opacity: 1; z-index: 2; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						src={angela.src}
						width={angela.width}
						height={angela.height}
						alt='angela jeweller'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						inferSize={true}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>Multilingual</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://angela.co.za/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s1'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						inferSize={true}
						src={dvmakeup.src}
						alt="dvmakeup'"
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						width={dvmakeup.width}
						height={dvmakeup.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>Multilingual</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://dvmakeup.com/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s2'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						inferSize={true}
						src={freedom.src}
						alt='freedom hill restaurant'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						width={freedom.width}
						height={freedom.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>xhtml, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://freedomhill-live.co.za/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s3'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						layout='responsive'
						src={mercer}
						alt='mecer express'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						loading='lazy'
						width={mercer.width}
						height={mercer.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>Joomla CMS</li>
						<li>xhtml, CSS3</li>
						<li>eCommerce</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://mecerexpresstore.co.za/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s4'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						src={auret.src}
						alt='olivari auret'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						inferSize={true}
						width={auret.width}
						height={auret.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://olivariauret.com/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s5'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						src={pxsecurity.src}
						alt='pxsecurity'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						inferSize={true}
						width={pxsecurity.width}
						height={pxsecurity.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>Design &amp; Development</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://pxsecurity.co.uk/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s6'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						inferSize={true}
						src={simapro.src}
						alt='simapro'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						style='opacity: 1;'
						width={simapro.width}
						height={simapro.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://simapro.co.za/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s7'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						inferSize={true}
						src={green.src}
						alt='the green house'
						style='opacity: 1;'
						width={green.width}
						height={green.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://tgh.co.za/' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
				<li
					class='overlay'
					id='rslides1_s8'
					style='float: none; position: absolute; opacity: 0; z-index: 1; display: list-item; transition: opacity 1000ms ease-in-out;'
				>
					<Picture
						src={renderroom.src}
						inferSize={true}
						alt='the render room'
						formats={['avif', 'webp']}
						style='opacity: 1;'
						width={renderroom.width}
						height={renderroom.height}
					/>
					<ul class='theoverlay'>
						<li>WordPress CMS</li>
						<li>HTML5, CSS3</li>
						<li>jQuery</li>
						<li>PHP, MySQL</li>
						<li>
							<a href='http://renderroom.co.za/v1' target='_blank'>visit site</a>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul><a href='#' class='rslides_nav rslides1_nav prev'>_</a><a
				href='#'
				class='rslides_nav rslides1_nav next'>""</a
			>
		</li>
	</ul>
</BaseLayout>

<script is:inline>
	setTimeout(() => {
		$('.rslides').responsiveSlides({
			auto: true,
			speed: 1000,
			timeout: 4000,
			pager: false,
			nav: true,
			random: false,
			pause: true,
			pauseControls: false,
			prevText: '&#x005f;',
			nextText: '&#x0022;',
			maxwidth: '',
			controls: '',
			namespace: 'rslides'
		})
	}, 5000)
</script>

<style>
	div,
	span,
	h2,
	p,
	a,
	img,
	ul,
	li {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		border: 0;
		font-size: 100%;
		font: inherit;
		vertical-align: baseline;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #fff;
	}
	ul {
		list-style: none;
	}
	h2 {
		font-weight: normal;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 35px;
		line-height: 40px;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}
	p {
		margin: 0 0 20px 0;
	}
	a,
	a:visited {
		color: #444;
		text-decoration: none;
		outline: 0;
	}
	a:hover,
	a:focus {
		color: #555;
	}
	ul {
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}
	ul {
		list-style: none outside;
	}
	ul ul {
		margin: 4px 0 5px 30px;
		font-size: 90%;
	}
	ul ul li {
		margin-bottom: 6px;
	}
	li {
		line-height: 1.5em;
	}
	li p {
		line-height: 31px;
	}
	ul.tabs {
		display: block;
		margin: 0 0 20px 0;
		padding: 0;
	}
	ul.tabs li {
		display: block;
		width: 33%;
		max-width: 150px;
		height: 30px;
		padding: 0;
		float: left;
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}
	ul.tabs li a {
		font-family: arial;
		display: block;
		text-decoration: none;
		width: auto;
		height: 29px;
		padding: 0 20px;
		line-height: 30px;
		-webkit-border-radius: 0 10px 0 0;
		-moz-border-radius: 0 10px 0 0;
		border-radius: 0 10px 0 0;
		border-right: solid 1px #aaa;
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 13px;
		text-shadow: 0 2px 3px #fff;
		background: rgb(0, 0, 0);
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

		background: linear-gradient(
			to top,
			rgba(145, 145, 145, 0.3) 0%,
			rgba(246, 246, 246, 0) 92%,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%
		);
	}
	ul.tabs li a.active {
		background: rgb(255, 255, 255);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);

		background: linear-gradient(
			to top,
			rgba(145, 145, 145, 0.3) 0%,
			rgba(254, 254, 254, 0.5) 73%,
			rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) 74%
		);
	}
	ul.tabs li:first-child a.active {
		margin-left: 0;
	}
	ul.tabs li:first-child a {
		border-width: 1px 1px 0 1px;
		-moz-border-radius-topleft: 2px;
		-webkit-border-top-left-radius: 2px;
		border-top-left-radius: 2px;
	}
	ul.tabs-content {
		margin: 0;
		display: block;
	}
	ul.tabs-content > li {
		display: none;
	}
	ul.tabs-content > li.active {
		display: block;
	}
	ul.tabs:before,
	ul.tabs:after {
		content: '\0020';
		display: block;
		overflow: hidden;
		visibility: hidden;
		width: 0;
		height: 0;
	}
	ul.tabs:after {
		clear: both;
	}
	ul.tabs {
		zoom: 1;
	}
	img {
		opacity: 0;
		zoom: 1;
	}
	[class^='icon-']:before {
		font-family: 'gregasaurus';
		font-style: normal;
		speak: none;
	}
	.icon-cannon:before {
		content: '\0032';
	}
	.icon-arrow-up:before {
		content: '\0043';
	}
	p {
		letter-spacing: 1px;
		text-align: justify;
	}
	h2 {
		font-family: 'MuncieRegular';
		color: #847e70;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 45px;
		margin-bottom: 25px;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}
	* {
		position: relative;
	}
	.container .insidecolumn {
		border: solid 1px #ccc;
		-webkit-border-radius: 10px 2px 10px 2px;
		-moz-border-radius: 10px 2px 10px 2px;
		border-radius: 10px 2px 10px 2px;
		background: rgb(255, 255, 255);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		padding: 10px 15px;
		-webkit-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		-moz-box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}
	.rslides {
		position: relative;
		list-style: none;
		overflow: hidden;
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.rslides_nav.rslides1_nav.next {
		float: right;
	}
	.rslides li {
		position: absolute;
		display: none;
		width: 100%;
		left: 0;
		top: 0;
	}
	.rslides > li:first-child {
		position: relative;
		display: block;
		float: left;
	}
	.rslides img {
		display: block;
		height: auto;
		float: left;
		width: 100%;
		border: 0;
	}

	.rslides_nav {
		font-family: 'gregasaurus';
	}
	.rslides_nav {
		position: relative;
	}
	.next {
		float: right;
	}
	.overlay {
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.overlay:hover .theoverlay {
		bottom: 0;
		-webkit-transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
		-moz-transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
		-o-transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
		-ms-transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
		transition: all 1s ease-in-out;
	}
	.theoverlay {
		height: 40%;
		background: rgb(0, 0, 0);
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
		bottom: -40%;
		position: absolute;
		width: 100%;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.rslides .theoverlay li:first-child {
		margin-top: 25px;
	}
	.rslides .theoverlay li {
		display: block;
		position: static;
		margin: 5px 0 0 2%;
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #000;
		line-height: 1em;
	}
	.theoverlay li a {
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 30px;
		font-style: italic;
		font-weight: normal;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px #000;
	}
	.theoverlay li a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	@media only screen and (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 959px) {
		.rslides .theoverlay li:first-child {
			margin-top: 5px;
		}
	}
	@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {
		.mobile-hide {
			display: none !important;
		}
	}
	@media only screen and (min-width: 480px) and (max-width: 767px) {
		p {
			font-size: 16px;
			line-height: 26px;
		}
	}
	@media only screen and (max-width: 479px) {
		.small-mobile-hide {
			display: none !important;
		}
		p {
			font-size: 14px;
			line-height: 23px;
		}
		.container .insidecolumn {
			padding-top: 10px;
		}
		ul.tabs li a {
			font-size: 13px;
			line-height: 1em;
		}
		.theoverlay {
			position: relative;
			background: none;
		}
		.rslides .theoverlay li,
		.rslides .theoverlay li a {
			color: #444;
			font-size: 13px;
			text-shadow: none;
		}
		.rslides_nav {
			position: absolute;
			top: 55px;
		}
		.rslides_nav.rslides1_nav.next {
			right: 0;
		}
		li p {
			line-height: 18px;
		}
	}
	/*! CSS Used fontfaces */
</style>
